Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.04,0:00:07.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,《烈探雷徹》前情提要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Previously on Reacher...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.04,0:00:10.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管你朋友卷入的是什么事 其金額都大到害死了他們\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, whatever your friends were involved in was big enough to get them killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.05,0:00:12.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我招募的托尼斯旺 絕對不可能參與此事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's no way the Tony Swan I recruited is a part of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.97,0:00:16.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來斯旺的職位是安全總監助理\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Seems Swan's title was assistant director of security.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.22,0:00:19.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“謝恩蘭斯頓 安全總監”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"Shane Langston. Director of Security."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.68,0:00:21.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許在大西洋城 跟我通話的就是這個人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maybe he's the guy I got on the phone in Atlantic City.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.93,0:00:23.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們得跟馬爾科姆拉沃伊談談\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We need to talk to Malcolm Lavoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.23,0:00:26.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們永遠沒法接近參議員 從他口中套話\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We'll never get close enough to a senator to find out what he may or may not know.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.61,0:00:30.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不需要接近他 丹尼爾博伊德 拉沃伊參議員的立法主任\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, we don't need to. Daniel Boyd, Senator Lavoy's legislative director.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.07,0:00:33.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小翅膀可以擊中空中的任何物體\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Little Wing can knock anything out of the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.28,0:00:35.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新時代有兩個基地\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}New Age has two bases.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.20,0:00:38.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,軟件是在紐約開發的 硬件是在丹佛的制造工廠制造的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Software made in New York, hardware at a manufacturing plant in Denver.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.33,0:00:39.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的指令是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What are our directives?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.54,0:00:42.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和迪克森去丹佛 奧唐納和我會去華盛頓特區\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You and Dixon go to Denver. O'Donnell and I will head down to D.C.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.87,0:00:45.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想去國土安全局 看看他們是否知道AM的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Want to swing by Homeland, see what they know about A.M.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.58,0:00:46.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給馬備好鞍\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Saddle up...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.00,0:00:50.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我們要去做一大堆牛仔的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...'cause we're about to do a whole lot of cowboy shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.51,0:00:56.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.89,0:01:01.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別鬧了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Quit it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.81,0:01:03.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會抓住你的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm gonna get you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.68,0:01:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 你抓不到的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, you're not.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.10,0:01:07.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別再丟我的泰迪熊了 否則我會...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't drop my teddy ever again or I will...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.69,0:01:09.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...你的臉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...at your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.19,0:01:13.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.61,0:01:16.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你帶腎上腺素筆了嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You got the EpiPens? 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.11,0:01:17.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 當然帶了 - 伍比呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Yes, of course. - And woobie? 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.41,0:01:20.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伍比毯 熊貓朋友 猴子林賽 全都裝好了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Woobie, Panda-pal, Lindsay the Monkey, they're all packed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.16,0:01:22.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶上一次性手機 別跟任何人聯系 不要找你父母\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Grab the burner phone. No contact with anyone. Not your parents,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.87,0:01:25.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且千萬別聯系你姐姐 她什么都往臉書上發\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and definitely not your sister. She puts everything on Facebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.37,0:01:26.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道這一套\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know the drill.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.87,0:01:28.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去阿什維爾 帶男孩們過去 那里有很多事做\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Go to Asheville. Take the boys. Plenty for you to do there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.92,0:01:30.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是旅游勝地 你會融入其中\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's touristy. You'll blend in.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.34,0:01:32.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用現金和現收現付信用卡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Use cash and this pay-as-you-go credit card.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.42,0:01:35.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按從一到十打分 情況有多糟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Scale of one to ten, how bad is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.59,0:01:37.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們不會去找你們的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They're not gonna come after you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.13,0:01:39.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們只是謹慎行事 額外小心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're just playing it safe. Belts and suspenders.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.68,0:01:40.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按從一到十打分\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}One to ten.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.85,0:01:44.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對于你們來說 最多四分\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}For you guys? Four, tops.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.31,0:01:46.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.35,0:01:48.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們正在處理一些相當壞的家伙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, we're dealing with some pretty bad guys, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.73,0:01:51.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我有朋友在身邊 我們會沒事的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I got the gang with me. We'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.07,0:01:52.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過幾天就結束了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It'll be over in a couple of days, promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.48,0:01:53.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得讓孩子做好準備\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I got to get the baby ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.94,0:01:56.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像上次一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.82,0:02:00.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我的泰迪熊還給我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Give my tie back!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.95,0:02:01.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我需要你們去...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I need...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.83,0:02:02.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她并不驚慌\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She doesn't panic.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.99,0:02:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...去挑你們的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.20,0:02:06.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既來之 則安之\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Accepts reality on reality's terms.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.08,0:02:08.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是急診室護士 和芝加哥消防隊長的女兒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Daughter of an ER nurse, Chicago fire chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.96,0:02:10.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常堅強\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tough as they come.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.17,0:02:12.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漂亮 堅強 聰明\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Beautiful, tough, smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.21,0:02:13.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她打賭輸了才嫁給你的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She lose a bet?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.92,0:02:16.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是我在做的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...dinner. That's what I'm making.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.84,0:02:19.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果當初有人問我 你的結局會是怎樣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If someone asked me back in the day where I thought you'd wind up,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.97,0:02:21.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會預測你因為淋病慢慢死去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'd have predicted a slow death from gonorrhea
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.93,0:02:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還會有六個女朋友 為了一輛04年的馬自達大打出手\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and a half dozen girlfriends fighting over an '04 Miata.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.72,0:02:28.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 原來我并不想要 世界上的每一個女孩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, well, turns out I didn't want every girl in the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.19,0:02:29.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只想要對的那個\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}just the right one.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.52,0:02:33.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想稍微冷靜一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.11,0:02:37.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內格利和迪克森剛到丹佛的工廠\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Neagley and Dixon just got to the Denver plant.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.19,0:02:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 她們也許能拿到那些導彈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Good. Maybe they get ahold of those missiles
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.20,0:02:40.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的家人就不必離開太久\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and your family won't have to be gone long.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.12,0:02:43.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真慢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're a slowpoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.58,0:02:48.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.67,0:02:52.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離開幾天沒關系\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A few days wouldn't hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.80,0:02:57.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.76,0:03:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,科羅拉多州丹佛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.97,0:03:05.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,國防合約管理局一個月前來過這里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The DCMA was here a month ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.76,0:03:06.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 現在我們又回來了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, and now we're back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.97,0:03:09.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們可是政府監管的“皰疹” 總是神出鬼沒\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're the cold sores of government oversight.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.94,0:03:12.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在 請把你們的領班叫來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, if you please? Your foreman?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.10,0:03:13.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新時代科技 配送倉庫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.73,0:03:14.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這里等著\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.40,0:03:20.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是讓我驚嘆不已 你拿著寫字板 表現自然\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Never ceases to amaze me how far you can get into a place
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.82,0:03:24.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就好像你就應該在那兒一樣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}if you just act like you're supposed to be there and carry a clipboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.20,0:03:29.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得怎么樣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How you feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.29,0:03:31.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sore.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.58,0:03:34.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿著高跟鞋打架 是需要一段時間適應的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, fighting in heels takes some getting used to.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.67,0:03:37.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿高跟鞋走路 也需要一段時間適應 我從來沒穿過\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Walking in heels takes some getting used to. Never wore 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.92,0:03:40.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你之前從來不穿高跟鞋\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You never wore heels?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.63,0:03:41.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不穿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.93,0:03:43.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連學校舞會上都不穿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not even to a school dance?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.68,0:03:45.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從沒去過\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Never went to one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.10,0:03:48.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不學習 或者不照顧我爸的時候 我得去工作\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When I wasn't studying or taking care of my dad, I had to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.10,0:03:54.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是糟糕的音樂 溫暖的酒水 以及一些摸著你的黏糊糊的手\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, bad music, warm punch and some clammy hands feeling you up...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.65,0:03:55.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你并沒有錯過太多\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you didn't miss much.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.90,0:04:03.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒人跟我說你們要來檢查\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nobody told me about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.28,0:04:06.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我們提前通知就不是突擊檢查了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wouldn't be a surprise inspection if we called ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.58,0:04:09.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山姆大叔想確定 你們把錢用在了正道上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Uncle Sam wants to make sure you're using his money wisely.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.62,0:04:13.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我們來看看小翅膀肩扛式發射器\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So we're here to take a look at Little Wing shoulder-fired launchers and missiles.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.17,0:04:16.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及導彈 檢查它們的規格和制造協議\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The specs, the manufacturing protocols,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.71,0:04:18.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,訂單以及交貨時間表\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the order and delivery schedules...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.67,0:04:20.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交貨時間表\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Delivery schedule?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.30,0:04:23.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交貨時間就在十分鐘前\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ten minutes ago. That's the delivery schedule.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.47,0:04:25.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有貨物剛運出去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The whole lot just went out the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.97,0:04:28.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總共650個\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All 650 of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.60,0:04:31.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,650\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}650?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.02,0:04:32.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是相關文件\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Here's the paperwork.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.27,0:04:36.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有人先給我打電話 我本可以推遲交貨 給你們留著\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If someone had called me first, I'd have held them for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.15,0:04:42.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 糟了 - 是啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Shit. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.35,0:05:14.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.81,0:05:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你需要幫忙嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You need an extra set of hands?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.40,0:05:17.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我需要的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What I need
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.02,0:05:18.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你的卡車\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}is your truck.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.10,0:05:53.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爆炸槍彈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.36,0:06:03.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切按計劃進行中\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're in business.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.57,0:06:12.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,匿名來電
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.83,0:06:15.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴我好消息吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Give me good news.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.08,0:06:18.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GPS追蹤器完成了其使命 你在新時代的同事們還不錯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}GPS tracker did the job. Your associates at New Age came through.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.21,0:06:21.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我殺了司機 他們可能會傷心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They might be upset I killed the driver, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.29,0:06:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要他們能拿到錢就不會在意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, they won't care so long as they get paid.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.80,0:06:26.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永遠不要低估貪婪的力量\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Never underestimate the power of greed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.59,0:06:29.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 換車上路吧 - 好的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Switch the trailers and get on the road. Will do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.38,0:06:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們紐約見\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Meet you in New York.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.56,0:06:35.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿扎里馬哈茂德
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.47,0:06:36.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這里這個名字\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This name, right here...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.81,0:06:38.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿扎里馬哈茂德\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...Azhari Mahmoud.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.44,0:06:44.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我們在丹佛 追捕的那個阿倫米克洛斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, the Aaron Miklos we were chasing down in Denver,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.57,0:06:45.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是馬哈茂德\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that was Mahmoud?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.98,0:06:47.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我們一直叫他“AM”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, we've been calling him "A.M."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.86,0:06:51.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這家伙很聰明 從未被捕 也沒有照片\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Guy's smart. Never been caught, no photos.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.12,0:06:54.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們甚至都不確定他的國籍\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hell, we're not even sure what nationality he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.83,0:06:56.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從我們對他僅有的了解來看\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}From the little bit we know of him,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.16,0:06:58.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他可以偽裝成中美洲人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}he can supposedly pass for Central American,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.58,0:07:00.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意大利人 希臘人 中東人...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Italian, Greek, Middle Eastern.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.50,0:07:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他如幽靈一般\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's a ghost.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.50,0:07:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們有三段他的 簡短且無關痛癢的錄音\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We have three short, innocuous recordings of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.80,0:07:07.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音頻鑒定部證實是同一個人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Audio forensics matched it as the same guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.67,0:07:09.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他每次都會使用不同的身份\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Each time, he's using a different identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.72,0:07:10.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意識形態呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ideology?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.14,0:07:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有政治或宗教背景\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No political or religious affiliations.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.60,0:07:16.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對他而言 唯有金錢才是上帝 他為出價最高的人工作\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}His only god is money, and he works for the highest bidder.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.85,0:07:20.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他會接洽壞人 為他們提供做壞事所需的工具\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He hooks up bad actors with the tools they need for bad actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.19,0:07:23.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在六年前第一次 出現在我們的視線中\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}First popped up on our radar six years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.31,0:07:26.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在恐怖分子試圖 獲取實驗神經毒氣罐的時候\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Terrorist cell caught trying to acquire tanks of experimental nerve gas.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.07,0:07:29.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們逮捕了整個團隊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We scooped up the whole lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.03,0:07:30.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有人 除了馬哈茂德\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All of them except Mahmoud.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.57,0:07:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管他叫什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Or whatever his name is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.66,0:07:35.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幽靈\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ghost.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.00,0:07:40.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次購買本來應該用無記名債券\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This buy was supposed to happen with bearer bonds.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.46,0:07:42.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 逃稅者 洗錢者 和其他各種混蛋的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, financial instrument of choice for tax evaders,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.96,0:07:46.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首選金融工具\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}money launderers and other assorted assholes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.13,0:07:48.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美國財政部在80年代 就停止發行這些債券了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The U.S. Treasury stopped issuing those in the '80s.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.38,0:07:51.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些國家仍在使用 那些是盧森堡的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Some countries still use them. Those were from Luxembourg.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.18,0:07:54.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像AM這么謹慎的人 會使用無記名債券\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Someone as cautious as A.M. would use bearer bonds.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.47,0:07:55.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果發行量足夠大\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If issued in large enough amounts,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.89,0:07:58.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以用公文包 攜帶一筆無法追蹤的財富\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you can carry an untraceable fortune in a briefcase.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.27,0:07:59.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,價值六千五百萬\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}65 million worth.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.77,0:08:00.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是問題所在\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's the problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.98,0:08:03.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你帶著一張無記名債券 就像帶著一百萬美元的鈔票\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You hold a bearer bond, that's like carrying a million dollar bill.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.60,0:08:04.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它歸持有者所有\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The bearer owns it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.81,0:08:08.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以AM不可能 讓除他以外的任何人運送酬勞\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So no way A.M. lets anyone deliver payment but him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.44,0:08:10.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是他的弱點\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's where he's vulnerable.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.20,0:08:12.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像你哥哥一樣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just like your brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.41,0:08:17.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當年我們辦案的時候 我問了喬\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Back when we worked the case, I asked Joe
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.66,0:08:19.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一些財務方面的問題\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}some questions of the financial side of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.49,0:08:21.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他也是你這么說的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He said same thing you just did.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.71,0:08:23.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,運送酬勞的會是AM 不會是其他人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A.M. will be the delivery boy. No one else.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.00,0:08:27.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 我們給你們 看了我們掌握的信息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay. We showed you ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.63,0:08:28.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在輪到你們了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now it's your turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.89,0:08:37.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們還在整理中\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We're still piecing it together, but, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.60,0:08:41.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我們向你們保證 等時機成熟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we give you our word, when this bird's cooked,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.39,0:08:42.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 我們會聯系你們 - 我保證\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- we'll reach out. - And you have my word
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.60,0:08:45.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不會再讓這家伙 逃出我們的手掌心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we won't let this guy slip through our fingers again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.23,0:08:46.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AM和他的所有同伙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A.M. and everyone working with him
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.77,0:08:49.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都將受到法律的最大制裁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}will be prosecuted to the fullest extent of the law.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.36,0:08:53.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除非我們先把他們都殺了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Unless we kill them all first.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.58,0:09:00.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你們\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thanks, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.96,0:09:08.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟他哥哥一樣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just like his brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.05,0:09:14.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\bord0\fs18\b1}烈探雷徹\N第二季第五集
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.05,0:09:14.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs21}本WEB版外掛字幕由  {\c&H9B30FF&}風吹來的那片云{\c&HFFFFFF&}  雙語合并
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.41,0:09:41.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,18輪車在這路上開不快的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}18-wheelers can't go that fast on these roads.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.62,0:09:43.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們有機會趕上他們\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We've got a decent shot at catching them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.25,0:09:49.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 尤其是他們中途停車了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, especially if they come to a stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.01,0:09:59.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些人是誰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who are these guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.22,0:10:01.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會告訴我們卡車壞了的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They're the guys who are gonna tell us the truck broke down 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.64,0:10:04.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且他們不得不 打電話叫另一個人來取車\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and they had to call another one to come pick up the trailer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.73,0:10:07.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但第二輛卡車不可能 在我們之前趕到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But no way a second truck got here before us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.52,0:10:08.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.10,0:10:10.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是劫車\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is a hijacking.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.52,0:10:13.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有可能你是錯的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Any chance you're wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.15,0:10:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒錯 他們怎么知道我們是誰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm not wrong! How the fuck did they know who we are?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.70,0:10:22.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,領班肯定給新時代打電話 說了兩個政府檢查員的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Foreman must've called New Age about two government inspectors.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.99,0:10:25.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭斯頓發現后給這些混蛋打了電話\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Langston finds out and calls these dickheads.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.21,0:11:12.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么鬼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The fuck?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.61,0:11:39.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得我們干掉他了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I think we got him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.28,0:11:40.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.15,0:11:43.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來我們還打中了 一個前胎和一個油箱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Also looks like we got a front tire and gas tank.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.45,0:11:49.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 我們離不開了 - 不 我去報警\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- We're not getting out of here. - No. I'll call the cops.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.58,0:11:51.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,匿名報警\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Make it anonymous.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.12,0:11:52.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Copy that. 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.08,0:11:55.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫我個忙 拿一下清單 我們需要把車牌取下來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do me a favor, grab the manifest. We need the license plate off of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.51,0:12:09.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.85,0:12:13.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 內格利\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What's up, Neagley?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.85,0:12:15.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實有很多事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hell of a lot, actually. 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.40,0:12:17.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們得說快點 因為警察 正在趕來統計尸體數量的路上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We got to talk fast, because cops are on the way to a body count 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.73,0:12:19.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們得拉開距離\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and we got to put some distance between us and them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.36,0:12:22.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么能證明你們在現場的東西嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Anything to put you at the scene?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.03,0:12:23.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,租的車\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Rental car.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.03,0:12:25.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它被射穿了 是用迪克森的假身份證租的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It was shot to hell, but it was rented with Dixon's fake ID.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.53,0:12:27.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們把它燒了 以免留下指紋和DNA\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We torched it to get rid of prints and DNA.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.41,0:12:29.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 所以發生了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Good. So what happened out there?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.54,0:12:31.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想聽壞消息 還是更壞的消息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You want the bad news or the worse news?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.33,0:12:32.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們大吃一驚吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Surprise us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.25,0:12:35.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一輛新時代的卡車 連同其運載的650枚導彈全被劫持了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, a New Age truck with all 650 missiles in it was hijacked.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.96,0:12:40.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 希望那是更壞的消息 - 恐怕不能如你所愿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I hope that's the worse news. You wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.13,0:12:41.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托尼斯旺還活著\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Tony Swan's alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.72,0:12:43.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 所以那是好消息啊 - 不是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- So that's a good thing. - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.34,0:12:45.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來斯旺還在替新時代做事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It looks like Swan's still working with New Age.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.59,0:12:48.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提貨單上顯示 是斯旺簽字授權送貨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}According to the bill of lading, Swan personally signed off on the shipment
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.51,0:12:49.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后貨物才離開工廠的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}before it left the factory.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.81,0:12:50.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那他在丹佛\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So he's in Denver?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.89,0:12:53.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文件上顯示他是從紐約授權的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, the paperwork said he authorized it from New York.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.06,0:12:54.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以他們偽造了他的簽名\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So they forged his signature.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.90,0:12:57.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 是數字指紋 - 那就是他們強迫了他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- It's a digital thumbprint. - Then they forced him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.56,0:13:00.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新時代紐約分部的門上有虹膜掃描儀\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}New Age New York has iris scanners on the doors,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.11,0:13:01.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,計算機是用的指紋鎖\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}thumbprint locks on the computers.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.44,0:13:03.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任何人都無法強迫托尼斯旺\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's no way that anyone could force Tony Swan
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.82,0:13:07.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通過復雜的生物識別技術 而不引起騷亂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}through that maze of biometrics without causing a huge scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.41,0:13:09.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有一個辦法能讓他們不擔心騷亂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The only way they wouldn't worry about a ruckus
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.53,0:13:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是讓所有一千多名員工 全都參與此事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}is if all thousand-plus employees were in on this thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.50,0:13:14.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這么大規模的陰謀的幾率...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and the odds of a conspiracy that vast are...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.54,0:13:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,微乎其微\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Minimal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.63,0:13:20.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你想相信斯旺是清白的 老大 我們都想相信\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know you want to believe Swan's clean, boss, we all do,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.67,0:13:24.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但就目前的情況看來不是這樣 等我們安全了再聊 好嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but things look the way they look. Talk when we're safe, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.38,0:13:27.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷徹\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Reacher?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.80,0:13:30.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Copy that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.06,0:13:34.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你之前說要把他們都殺了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So what you said about killing them all...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.10,0:13:37.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那包括托尼斯旺嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...that include Tony Swan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.61,0:13:43.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去散步\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm going for a walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.33,0:13:56.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們不需要這些\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You boys won't be needing these.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.62,0:13:59.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 我們這兒都是朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, we're all friends here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.88,0:14:03.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿走了他們的槍\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Took their guns.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.96,0:14:06.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要他們找不到斯旺身上的竊聽器\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Long as they didn't find the wire Swan's wearing,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.22,0:14:07.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就一切安好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we're five by five.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.47,0:14:08.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像那個惡棍說的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Like that miscreant said,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.89,0:14:10.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“我們這兒都是朋友”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"We're all friends here."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.26,0:14:14.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 我們看看你有什么 美國兵 - 美國兵\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's see what you got, G.I. Joe. G.I. Joe?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.18,0:14:15.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說山地大猩猩更貼切吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}More like Mighty Joe Young.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.93,0:14:19.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想不想和這個大塊頭 擠在一個散兵坑里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How'd you like to be jammed into a foxhole with this giant motherfucker?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.02,0:14:20.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的價格比你們現在付的更優惠\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We'll beat whatever price you're paying now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.73,0:14:24.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的供應商可以從 無法談判的海外源頭\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Our supplier can get you all the H you can move from an overseas source
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.11,0:14:26.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給你們弄來 所有你們可以轉運的海洛因\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that's in no position to negotiate terms.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.15,0:14:28.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們把省下來的錢都給你們\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We pass the savings on to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.75,0:14:45.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.46,0:14:47.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們來談談價錢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let's talk money.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.59,0:14:49.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們一達成協議 我們就出動\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Soon as they agree to a deal, we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.72,0:14:52.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逮捕他們 逼迫他們 他們會說出他們的貨源\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Bust them, lean on them, they give up their source;
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.35,0:14:54.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們逮捕他們 然后全都能升職\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we bust them, then we all get bumped.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.31,0:14:55.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸前的綬帶和獎章就更多了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}More fruit salad on our chests...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.72,0:14:57.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,薪水支票上還會有 更多美元標志哦 兄弟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}More dollar signs on our paychecks, bro.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.10,0:15:01.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什么要在我們的薪水支票上 加美元標志\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why would they add dollar signs to our paychecks?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.02,0:15:02.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴 弗朗茨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Shut up, Franzy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.19,0:15:05.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這孩子說得有道理 曼努埃爾 一個美元標志就夠了 重點是零\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The kid's got a point, Manuel. You only need one dollar sign.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.57,0:15:06.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Assholes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.86,0:15:08.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心 有人靠近\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Heads up. We got incoming.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.71,0:15:26.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早該來了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}About time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.84,0:15:31.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,110\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}110?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.68,0:15:33.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你之前說價格會優于我們目前的價格\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You said you could beat our current price.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.43,0:15:34.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我給你們優惠了啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I am beating it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.68,0:15:36.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不夠\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not by enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.51,0:15:38.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想讓我們更換供應商 那就打動我們吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You want us to change suppliers, motivate us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.77,0:15:39.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雞肉 我說的是豬肉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is chicken. I said pork.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.85,0:15:43.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 105怎么樣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay. Fucking idiots always get it wrong. How's 105?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.19,0:15:46.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽起來像是在浪費我的時間\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Sounds like you're wasting my fucking time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.32,0:15:48.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還找得到這么純賣105的嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You got forks? - You have another brick as pure as that for 105?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.44,0:15:50.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 我見過更好的 - 胡說\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Seen better. Bullshit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.15,0:15:51.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有一長串買家的名單\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I got a list of other buyers a mile long.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.86,0:15:53.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 我來找你是因為你的量... - 我認識你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- I came to you... - I know you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.66,0:15:55.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- ...值得我花時間協商 - 你認錯人了吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...because you purchase at a volume, which makes it worthwhile. I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.58,0:15:57.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒認錯 我從哪兒認識你的來著\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, I do. Where do I know you from?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.66,0:15:58.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Uh-oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.54,0:16:00.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 可能沒什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hold on. Might be nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.66,0:16:02.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 不知道 - 我知道我們以前見過\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- No idea. - Look, I have other offers coming in. - I know we've met before.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.92,0:16:07.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 你能為我做什么  - 一百 要么接受 要么就算了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What can you do for me? 100. Take it or leave it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.38,0:16:10.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是前不久買我吉他的那個人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I got it. You're the guy I sold my guitar to a while back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.10,0:16:16.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把我跟其他人搞混了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You got me mixed up with somebody else.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.51,0:16:18.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克雷格列表網 兄弟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Craigslist, dude.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.68,0:16:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你買了我的原聲吉他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You bought my acoustic.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.81,0:16:27.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是要吃飯敘舊 還是達成協議\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We gonna eat and discuss old times or are we gonna make a deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.44,0:16:30.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們這些混蛋不想要這些東西 我們有其他地方可以賣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You assholes don't want this stuff, we got other places we can sell it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.53,0:16:35.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 這家伙買吉他的時候\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wait a minute. Wait a minute, when this guy bought it,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.66,0:16:38.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他穿著憲兵的制服\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}he was in an Army cop uniform.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.67,0:16:53.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fuck. Go, go, go, go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.72,0:16:57.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.39,0:17:06.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 叫救護車  - 別開槍\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Call an ambulance! - Don't shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.81,0:17:09.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們有一名軍官倒下了 需要醫療救援\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We have an officer down. We need medical assistance.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.07,0:17:12.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 子彈沒打中你的心臟 - 但打碎了我的鎖骨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The bullet missed your heart. But shattered my collarbone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.53,0:17:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有段時間彈不了吉他了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not gonna be playing that guitar for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.70,0:17:16.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞翁失馬\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Every cloud...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.49,0:17:18.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去你的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fuck you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.16,0:17:20.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 你不能招惹誰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey, who don't you mess with?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.41,0:17:21.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡車駕駛員工會\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Teamsters?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.75,0:17:27.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我欠你一個人情\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I owe you one.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.52,0:17:46.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我猜猜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let me guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.48,0:17:50.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,政府牌照 政府制服 政府的車\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Government plates, government suits, government rides.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.48,0:17:52.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到拉沃伊議員花了這么長時間\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Surprised it took Senator Lavoy this long
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.61,0:17:54.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才查出昨晚是誰動了他的走狗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to figure out who sweated his flunky last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.07,0:17:57.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,參議員有個提議給你 上車\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The senator has a proposition for you. Get in.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.07,0:17:58.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.95,0:18:00.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什么 雷徹先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why not, Mr. Reacher?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.78,0:18:02.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我雷徹\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just "Reacher."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.91,0:18:06.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 雷徹 你為什么不上車\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fine, Reacher. Why won't you get in the car?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.33,0:18:08.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為他語氣不善\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because he didn't ask nicely.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.04,0:18:10.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.17,0:18:12.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈特 那個神奇的詞是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hart, what's the magic word?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.13,0:18:17.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你上車\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Please get in the vehicle?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.73,0:18:35.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在丹佛的人帶著貨物僥幸逃脫\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My man in Denver barely got away with the merchandise.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.11,0:18:38.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我為了實現無縫交易 付出了額外的代價\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm paying a premium for a seamless transaction,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.28,0:18:41.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且目前為止 這已經算不上是無縫交易了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and so far this has been anything but seamless.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.41,0:18:44.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果這些問題持續存在 那可能得調整價格了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If these problems persist, there may have to be a price adjustment.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.83,0:18:47.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯旺先生的一些老朋友 給我們帶來了麻煩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Some of Mr. Swan's old friends are causing us problems,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.66,0:18:49.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但沒什么是我們處理不了的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but it's nothing we can't handle.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.21,0:18:52.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你想要商品 就得遵守交易\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you want the merchandise, you honor the deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.55,0:18:55.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做你答應做的事 而我也會如此\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do what you promised and I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.34,0:18:58.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.05,0:18:59.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.97,0:19:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你現在在哪里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where are you now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.10,0:19:05.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就在外面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I am just outside...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.35,0:19:08.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 這不可能是真的吧 “弗倫奇利克”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, no, t-this can't be right. "French Lick"?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.31,0:19:10.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他媽的美國人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fucking Americans.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.81,0:19:11.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,印第安納州\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Indiana.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.69,0:19:16.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 等你到達這里時 小翅膀的芯片\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay. The Little Wing chips will be ready to install
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.94,0:19:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會準備好安裝在導彈里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}in the missiles by the time you get here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.70,0:19:21.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯旺先生的同事們也會處理好的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And Mr. Swan's associates will be taken care of.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.41,0:19:23.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,計劃已經開始實施了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That plan's already in motion.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.24,0:19:27.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去他媽的英國佬\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fuck your king.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.58,0:19:29.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蠢貨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Prick.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.46,0:19:32.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,華盛頓特區史密森國家動物園
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.42,0:19:40.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在靈長類動物展示區的后面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Backstage at the primate exhibit?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.72,0:19:43.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夠夸張的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Dramatic.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.09,0:19:45.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以為你們在大猩猩中間會很舒服\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Thought you might feel comfortable among the gorillas.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.89,0:19:49.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷徹先生 我是馬爾科姆拉沃伊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mr. Reacher, I'm Malcolm Lavoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.73,0:19:52.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 他更喜歡你叫他“雷徹” - 不\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- He prefers just "Reacher." - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.52,0:19:54.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他必須叫我“先生”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He has to call me "Mister."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.23,0:19:58.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷徹先生 很抱歉 我讓人用這種方式把你帶過來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My apologies for the manner in which you were brought in here, Mr. Reacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.74,0:20:01.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我猜你使用這個地方 是因為這是華盛頓特區為數不多的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Assume you use this location 'cause it's one of the few spots in D.C.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.86,0:20:04.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以在沒有人 監視或窺探的情況下見面的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}where you can meet without prying eyes or surveillance bugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.91,0:20:07.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是為什么我任命 自己為動物園董事會成員\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mm-hmm. It's why I got myself appointed to the zoo's board.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.87,0:20:11.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信你認識我的立法主任 博伊德先生吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ah, I believe you know my legislative director, Mr. Boyd.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.79,0:20:13.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.04,0:20:14.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是他喜歡可卡因\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}he's the one who likes cocaine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.96,0:20:17.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道發生了什么后\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know, when I found out what happened,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.42,0:20:19.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聯系了我在局里的一個朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I reached out to a friend of mine at the Bureau.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.42,0:20:21.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想象一下博伊德知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Imagine Boyd's embarrassment when he learned
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.34,0:20:24.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己一開始把我們的秘密透露給了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that the people he revealed our secrets to
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.93,0:20:26.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非聯邦特工有多尷尬\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}weren't FBI agents in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.85,0:20:31.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,監控錄像顯示你們進入了轄區\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Security video showed you entering the precinct
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.06,0:20:34.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面部識別軟件 將你和一個軍人的身份證相匹配\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and facial recognition software matched you to a military ID.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.98,0:20:37.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰克雷徹\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Jack Reacher. 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.15,0:20:41.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有中間名 西點軍校出身 兩枚銀星\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No middle name. West Point, two Silver Stars,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.03,0:20:44.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一枚銅星 一枚紫心勛章等等\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}a Bronze Star, Purple Heart and so on.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.07,0:20:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放尊重點\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Show some respect.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.66,0:20:49.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很多勛章啊 順便說一句 我想感謝你的服役\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That is quite a list, and I want to thank you for your service, by the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.99,0:20:53.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你退役后 像是從人間蒸發了一樣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Seems like after you retired, you kind of fell off the face of the Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.08,0:20:57.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了幾年前 在佐治亞州馬格雷夫的一起事件\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Except for this incident a couple years ago in Margrave, Georgia.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.34,0:21:00.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你被指控殺了自己的兄弟\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Charged with the murder of your own brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.55,0:21:03.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你當然被無罪釋放了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You were, of course, exonerated.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.84,0:21:06.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后 喬之前一直在調查的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then a massive counterfeiting operation
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.59,0:21:08.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個大規模偽造行動\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that Joe had been investigating
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.43,0:21:11.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實實在在地被燒毀了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}literally and figuratively burned to the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.47,0:21:13.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在 官方的說辭是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, the official story was
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.14,0:21:18.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那都是一個菜鳥警察 和一個外地退伍軍人干的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that it was all the work of a rookie cop and an out-of-town veteran.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.02,0:21:21.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是在波士頓逮捕了 博伊德的這位外地退伍軍人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The same out-of-town veteran that arrested Boyd here in Boston.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.32,0:21:25.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說重點吧 這里有股猴子屎的味道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Get to the point. Smells like monkey shit in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.36,0:21:28.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷徹先生 我知道馬格雷夫的事 是你做的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, I know it was you in Margrave, Mr. Reacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.66,0:21:32.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望針對我們目前的情況 你也能做同樣的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I want you to do the same thing for the situation we have here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.29,0:21:40.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.13,0:21:42.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為在波士頓 你暗示博伊德\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because in Boston, you insinuated to Boyd
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.34,0:21:46.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,軍隊和民用飛機 可能會因為小翅膀而陷入危險\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that military and civilian aircraft could be in danger due to Little Wing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.34,0:21:47.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在 我只能假設那意味著\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now, I can only assume that means that terrorists
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.84,0:21:49.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怖分子對這項技術很感興趣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}are interested in the tech,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.68,0:21:51.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在努力獲得它\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}working hard to obtain it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.01,0:21:53.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦我們確認了你的身份 我們就深入調查\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}See, once we identified you, we looked into things deeper
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.98,0:21:56.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們知道你以前的小隊又重組了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and we learned that your old unit's back together,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.81,0:21:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其中有些人死了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and some are dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.86,0:22:00.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別那么震驚 雷徹先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't look so shocked, Mr. Reacher,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.69,0:22:02.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是美國國會議員 我能把事情做好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm a U.S. congressman, I get things done.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.61,0:22:05.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很震驚 是因為 美國國會議員居然還能做事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm shocked because a U.S. congressman got anything done.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.61,0:22:10.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經習慣了 人們的陰陽怪氣 雷徹先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm used to the slings and arrows, Mr. Reacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.95,0:22:15.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的底線是想要這個武器的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But bottom line, the people who want this weaponry
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.08,0:22:17.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不能被允許持有該武器\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}can never be allowed to have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.62,0:22:20.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為如果有人知道你從一開始\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because if anyone knew you were involved in the shady dealings
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.59,0:22:24.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就參與了創造小翅膀的不正當交易 你就會被起訴\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that created Little Wing in the first place, you'd be indicted.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.21,0:22:26.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除掉壞人 讓我干干凈凈的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Get rid of the bad guys, keep my hands clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.59,0:22:28.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在華盛頓 我們稱之為雙贏\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In Washington, we call that a win-win.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.39,0:22:34.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我盡我所能 給予了我方捍衛民主所需的工具\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I did what I did to give our side the tools they need to defend democracy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.89,0:22:38.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是避免了繁文縟節 那些沒什么用 只會拖延時間\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I just avoided the typical red tape that does nothing but cause the delays
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.73,0:22:39.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,造成生命損失\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that cost lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.65,0:22:41.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還在這個過程中中飽私囊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And lined your pockets in the process.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.94,0:22:43.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再次重申 這叫雙贏\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Again, win-win.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.90,0:22:47.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想讓無辜群眾因為這種武器而死\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I don't want innocent people to die because of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.78,0:22:50.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是政客 不是怪物 雷徹先生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm a political animal, I'm not a monster, Mr. Reacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.99,0:22:53.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我不是請你幫忙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I'm not asking for your help,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.95,0:22:55.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是給你提供幫助\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm offering you mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.16,0:22:58.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是那種喜歡把事情做好的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're the kind of man who likes to gets things done, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.04,0:23:00.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在軍隊和馬格雷夫的記錄 證明了這一點\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your record in the military, and in Margrave, proves that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.42,0:23:02.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜歡打亂計劃\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You like to upset the apple cart.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.96,0:23:06.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我準備給予你所需要的一切 協助你完成這項任務\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, I'm prepared to give you whatever you need to aid you in that endeavor.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.47,0:23:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等你完工后\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And when you're done,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.55,0:23:12.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有人能證明你曾卷入過那些計劃\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}no one will be able to prove that you were ever near those apples in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.64,0:23:16.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就把這些東西砸成碎片\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just smash this thing to bits.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.47,0:23:20.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這些人全都一網打盡 不遺留任何人威脅他人生命\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Leave no man left standing. No one left to endanger lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.65,0:23:24.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后你就又可以消失了 沒有人會繼續找你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And then you can disappear again. No one will go looking for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.69,0:23:26.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是你的朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Or your friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.76,0:23:54.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.60,0:23:56.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 不怎么快樂的巨人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey, Not-So-Jolly Green Giant.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.64,0:23:57.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已經把那套衣服扔了嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You throw away that suit yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.97,0:23:59.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有 怎么了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.48,0:24:01.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驗尸官終于歸還了弗朗茨的尸體\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Coroner finally released Franz's body.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.23,0:24:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葬禮在明天舉行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Funeral's tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.60,0:24:05.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們得回紐約\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We got to go back to New York.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.49,0:24:16.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葬禮
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.49,0:24:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我讓我的辦公室做了一些零星的調查\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Had my office make some discrete inquiries.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.20,0:24:22.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹佛的警察發現了 被槍擊的卡車和被掉包的拖車\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Denver sheriffs found the shot-up truck with a switched-out trailer.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.08,0:24:24.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 里面什么都沒有 只有幾塊磚 - 它們完美匹配\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nothing in it but crates of bricks. Guessing they perfectly matched
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.71,0:24:26.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發射器和導彈的重量\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}the weight of the launchers and the missiles.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.88,0:24:29.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 看來他們的計劃 是開車將假的貨物\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yep. It seems their plan was to drive the dummy cargo down
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.26,0:24:30.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,運送到洛杉磯港口\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to the port in L.A.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.63,0:24:32.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后送到菲律賓的軍事基地\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And ship it to an Army base in the Philippines 
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.68,0:24:34.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者任何那武器應該去的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}or wherever the weapons were supposed to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.89,0:24:37.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據我們的資料顯示 是韓國\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}South Korea, according to the documents we saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.26,0:24:39.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真聰明\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.18,0:24:42.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貨船從西海岸到那里 需要三到四周的時間\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Three to four weeks for a cargo ship to get there from the West Coast,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.48,0:24:45.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在另一邊開箱前 沒人知道武器失蹤了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}no one knows the weapons were missing till they open it up on the other end.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.23,0:24:47.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道那要多長時間呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And who knows how long that could be?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.19,0:24:50.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,軍隊可能會直接將其放到倉庫 幾個月都不看它們\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Army could just load it into storage and not see them again for months.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.11,0:24:51.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到那時 為時已晚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And by then, it's too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.99,0:24:53.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怖分子已經擊落了數十架飛機\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Terrorists have taken down dozens of planes
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.61,0:24:55.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我們還不知道 他們從哪兒弄來的武器\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and we have no idea where they got the firepower.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.45,0:24:57.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起武器\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Speaking of firepower,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.07,0:24:59.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有任何關于真正的導彈的 去向的線索嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we have any leads as to where the real missiles went?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.24,0:25:02.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,科羅拉多州警方在丹佛外的 一塊田里發現了那輛卡車 是空的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Colorado State Police found the truck in a field outside Denver. It was empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.96,0:25:04.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據卡車在泥土里的痕跡來看\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Based on the tracks in the dirt,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.37,0:25:07.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們認為一架私人飛機 連夜把武器帶走了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}they think a private plane flew the weapons out overnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.25,0:25:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它可能會去往任何地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Could be headed here.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.75,0:25:12.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自從911以后 紐約上空就一直受到了密切地監控\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Since 9/11, they've kept a pretty close watch on New York's skies.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.01,0:25:13.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們知道AM很謹慎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And we know A.M.'s cautious.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.93,0:25:15.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我是他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I were him,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.22,0:25:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會把它們帶到 賓夕法尼亞州的某個小機場里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'd fly them into some small airstrip in Pennsylvania,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.60,0:25:19.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也可以是新罕布什爾州 再開車將武器運到紐約\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}maybe New Hampshire, then drive the weapons into New York
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.97,0:25:21.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好給它們加上小翅膀軟件\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to load them up with the Little Wing software.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.93,0:25:22.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,言之有理\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.85,0:25:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們需要知道導彈 到底是在往哪兒運才能攔截它們\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We need to know exactly where the missiles are headed so we can intercept them.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.60,0:25:28.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為當錢易手時\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}'Cause when the money changes hands,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.77,0:25:31.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AM會到場 殺了我們的人的兇手也在\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A.M. will be there, and so will the people who killed our guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.74,0:25:40.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷徹 你看到那玩意了嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Reacher. You seeing this shit?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.16,0:25:44.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是那天他車里的玩具嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Isn't that that toy he had in his car the other day?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.71,0:25:47.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米奇 我的侄子也有一個\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mikey. My nephews have the same one.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.58,0:25:51.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是個很棒的玩具 我們一直一起玩\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's a great toy. We play with it all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.34,0:25:56.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我小時候 我有海王\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}When I was a kid, I had Aquaman.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.51,0:26:00.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得他跟魚說話的方式太酷了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I thought it was so cool how he could talk to fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.81,0:26:03.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我當時也想跟我的狗說話\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}'Cause I wanted to talk to my dog, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.02,0:26:11.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.11,0:26:17.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想把這張照片給你 這是我的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I want you to have this, too. This was mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.20,0:26:19.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣杰羅姆\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Saint Jerome.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.37,0:26:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是爸爸或媽媽去了天堂的 孩子的守護神\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He's the patron saint of kids whose moms and dads go to heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.75,0:26:26.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望你每晚都念\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I want you to say the prayer...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.62,0:26:31.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這照片后面的祈禱詞\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}...on the back, every night.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.01,0:26:35.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它會讓你爸離你近點\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It'll help keep your dad close.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.47,0:26:40.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能做到嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Can you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.51,0:26:44.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Good boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.89,0:26:47.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Good boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.77,0:26:52.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有任何需要 就給我打電話\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You need anything, you call me.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.82,0:26:55.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白天晚上都行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Day or night.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.48,0:26:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 謝謝 - 沒事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Thank you. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.03,0:27:00.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 米奇 葬禮要開始了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come on, Mikey. They're just about to start.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.41,0:27:06.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什么要送玩具 給我死去的朋友的兒子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why are you giving toys to my dead friend's son?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.75,0:27:07.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.87,0:27:12.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和孩子相處融洽 就能刷媽媽的好感度\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Cozy up to the kid, score points with Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.79,0:27:15.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看到一個悲傷的寡婦 心想:“這個目標容易得手”\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You see a grieving widow and think, "Easy target"?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.96,0:27:21.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你現在在跟我開玩笑嗎  你是想找死嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you kidding me right now? You got some kind of death wish?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.05,0:27:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些人這么想\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Some people think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.60,0:27:23.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是來表達敬意的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm here to pay my respects.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.68,0:27:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什么昨晚在波士頓 有一個摩托車團伙攻擊我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Why did a biker gang take a run at me in Boston last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.60,0:27:27.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你是個混蛋\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}'Cause you're an asshole.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.52,0:27:31.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能吧 也可能是因為 我們只把我們的行蹤告訴了你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Possibly. Or maybe it's 'cause you're the only person I told  we were going there.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.31,0:27:34.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 你是想說我是黑警\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wait, wait, wait. Are you trying to say that I'm bent?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.98,0:27:36.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什么都沒想說\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not trying to say anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.15,0:27:42.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道我為什么跟米奇說話嗎  因為我知道他在經歷什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You know why I was talking to Mikey? Because I know what he's going through.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.66,0:27:45.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道每晚看著窗戶外面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know what it is to look out the window every night
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.28,0:27:48.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祈禱街上來的是自己父親的車 是什么感覺\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and pray that the next set of headlights coming down the street is your father's car,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.37,0:27:50.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使你知道那永遠不會發生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}even though you know it'll never happen,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.71,0:27:53.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你親眼看到 羅馬諾殯儀館的那些家伙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}because you saw the guys from Romano's funeral home
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.21,0:27:55.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在他的棺材上撒土\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}throw dirt on his casket.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.13,0:27:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道失去家人是什么感覺嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you know what it is to lose family?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.30,0:27:59.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 他們都死了 全都死了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, they're all dead. Every one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.84,0:28:01.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我在說你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I was talking about you,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.59,0:28:03.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 沒說你爸 - 我在說他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}not your father. I'm talking about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.51,0:28:06.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爸曾是一名警察 一個好警察\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My father was a cop, a good one,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.14,0:28:09.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他拒絕受賄 因此被人殺害\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and he refused to be on the take and they killed him for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.52,0:28:14.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽著\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.77,0:28:17.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道那是 你朋友的兒子和遺孀 我懂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know that's your friend's son and widow. I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.73,0:28:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但如果你再說我是黑警\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But you call me dirty one more time,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.90,0:28:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不在乎我們是否是站在圣母像面前\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and I don't care if we're standing in front of the statue of the Holy Mother,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.20,0:28:25.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會新賬老賬一起算 就在這里狠狠揍你一頓\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I will give you that beating that I owe you right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.95,0:28:29.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一 只要你想 我隨時奉陪\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}One, I'll take that fight any time you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.00,0:28:30.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And two...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.87,0:28:34.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道你父親的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I didn't know that about your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.42,0:28:36.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 你不知道的事可多了去了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, well, what you don't know could fill the Javits.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.04,0:28:39.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為天知道你在波士頓做什么的時候\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because while you were in Boston doing God knows what,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.80,0:28:42.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在忙著查新時代安保部的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was running those security names from New Age.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.09,0:28:44.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們全都是前紐約市警察局的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All former NYPD,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.22,0:28:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部來自第三分局\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}all from the 3rd precinct.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.80,0:28:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老板蘭斯頓和其他幾個人 都接受過內務部的調查\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The boss, Langston and a few other guys, they were under investigation by IA.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.60,0:28:52.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們提前退休了 那些指控就消失了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They took early retirement and the charges went away.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.73,0:28:56.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后他們全都在新時代 找到了輕松的工作 雇傭了所有朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then they all got cushy jobs at New Age, and they hired all their pals along.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.44,0:28:58.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整個團隊全是黑警\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Whole team of bad cops?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.07,0:28:59.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有人 除了你的朋友 斯旺\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Everybody except your buddy Swan.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.78,0:29:02.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他是唯一一個有從軍經歷\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But he's the only one that has military experience
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.15,0:29:04.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道恐怖分子 想要哪種武器的人 所以...\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to know what type of weapons terrorists want, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.32,0:29:06.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在你在含沙射影地說 會讓我生氣的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Now you're implying something that's pissing me off.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.45,0:29:08.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不能否認這種猜想是合理的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You can't deny he makes sense for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.62,0:29:12.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據他的背景 這一切可能都是他主使的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}With his background, for all we know, he might have put the whole thing together.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.41,0:29:16.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有警察 全是黑警 都是一個轄區的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All cops, all bad, all from the same precinct.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.17,0:29:18.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 你審問過他們中任何人嗎  - 問不了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You interview any of them? - Couldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.63,0:29:20.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在他們辦公的地方砸出了一個大洞\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You turned their office into a drive-through.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.71,0:29:22.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們躲起來了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They went to the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.13,0:29:25.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們的住處空無一人 跟托尼斯旺的住處一樣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Their places were empty, just like Tony Swan's.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.01,0:29:29.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想罵某人是黑警  先查查你自己的后院吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You want to call somebody dirty? First look in your own backyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.73,0:29:42.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此 我們要將我們的兄弟 卡爾文弗朗茨埋葬\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We therefore commit our brother Calvin Franz to the ground,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.53,0:29:47.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歸于大地 塵歸塵 土歸土\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}earth to earth, ashes to ashes, dust to dust,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.53,0:29:51.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓往生者安寧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}in sure and certain hope of the resurrection
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.37,0:29:53.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓在世者重獲解脫 阿門\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to the eternal life.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.91,0:29:56.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿門\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Amen.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.53,0:30:25.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴槍隊 注意\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Firing party, attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.91,0:30:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待命\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Stand by.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.08,0:30:33.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.62,0:30:38.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞄準\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Aim.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.71,0:30:40.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開火\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.34,0:30:42.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.92,0:30:45.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞄準 開火\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Aim. Fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.09,0:30:51.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 趴下  - 開火\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Get down! - Fire...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.18,0:30:55.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我保護你們 快 我們走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I got you. Come on. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.89,0:30:57.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離開這里 快走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Get out of here. Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.27,0:30:59.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人開槍 快跑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Active shooters! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.23,0:31:01.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.45,0:31:17.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 幾個人  - 據我所知 兩個\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How many? As far as I can tell, two.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.29,0:31:20.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 在路對面 - 手槍沒用 得離近點\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Across the road. Handguns are useless from this distance. We got to get closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.25,0:31:22.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包抄他們 內格利和我 負責右邊的那個\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Flank them. Neagley and I will take the one on the right.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.46,0:31:25.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們倆負責左邊那個 上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You two take the one on the left. Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.74,0:31:50.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們盡可能接近 還不夠\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Close as we're gonna get. It's not enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.24,0:31:51.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以等警察來\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We could wait for the cops.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.78,0:31:55.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能讓他們跑了 他們一聽到警笛就會散開\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We can't let them get away. As soon as they hear sirens, they scatter.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.24,0:32:00.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 我來吸引火力 你去干掉他們\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right. I'll draw their fire, you take them out.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.54,0:32:02.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 我拒絕 - 你能做到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Negative. - You can do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.25,0:32:03.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你射得很準\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-You're a great shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.96,0:32:05.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你跑得很慢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But you're a slow runner.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.10,0:32:18.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去你的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Fuck this.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.02,0:32:20.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.71,0:32:47.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上車\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Get in!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.80,0:32:55.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你現在相信我了 還是饑不擇食了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, you trust me now, or are you just desperate?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.43,0:32:58.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看見你保護安吉拉和米奇 所以我猜你說的是真的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I saw you protect Angela and Mikey, so I guess you're playing it square.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.14,0:33:04.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你那兒有內鬼 那是肯定的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You got a rat in your house, though, that's for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.98,0:33:13.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽的 拉索 開快點\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Shit, Russo, it's the pedal on the right.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.15,0:33:14.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我做我的工作\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let me do my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.87,0:33:19.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抄近路\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Cut the corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.79,0:33:21.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 有路緣石 - 跳過去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- There's a curb. - Jump the curb!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.33,0:33:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能別管我怎么開車嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Will you climb out of my ass?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.55,0:33:32.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以為這應該是高速追逐戰\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I thought this was supposed to be a high-speed pursuit.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.64,0:33:43.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 我們最好的線索要被你搞丟了 - 你想來開車嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're losing our best lead. You want to drive?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.69,0:33:45.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.15,0:33:46.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hey, hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.25,0:34:10.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 你真他媽是個禍害  - 你開車像個瞎子一樣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're a fucking menace, you know that? You drive like you're blind.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.42,0:34:18.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別開槍 我受夠了 好嗎 我受夠了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't shoot. I'm done. Okay? I'm done.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.30,0:34:22.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 你被捕了 混蛋 - 不\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're under arrest, asshole. No.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.27,0:34:27.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些人在光天化日之下 攻擊我們 還是在人多的葬禮上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}These guys took a run at us in broad daylight at a crowded funeral.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.52,0:34:30.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們越來越絕望了 這意味著這事快到緊要關頭了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They're getting desperate. Means this thing's coming to a head fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.56,0:34:33.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們拘留他 他會請律師 在為時已晚前緘口不言\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We take him in, he lawyers up and doesn't talk until it's too late
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.44,0:34:36.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怖分子有650次機會 擊落一架商業客機\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and a terrorist has 650 chances to take down a commercial airliner.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.28,0:34:37.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你想讓我做什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, what do you want me to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.20,0:34:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看向另一邊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look the other way.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.24,0:34:45.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托 伙計\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, come on, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.21,0:34:50.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你不告訴我你知道的一切\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}By not telling me everything you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.79,0:34:52.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是在保護殺了我朋友的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you're protecting the people who killed my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.80,0:34:56.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會浪費時間 用那些審訊技巧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm not gonna waste my time with enhanced interrogation techniques.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.01,0:34:57.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只會奪走你的生命\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm just gonna squeeze the life out of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.76,0:35:02.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你在你死前 想完全卸下自己的負擔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, if at any point before you die you feel like fully unburdening yourself...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.97,0:35:04.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就眨眼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}blink.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.06,0:35:13.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 現在說話 - 好的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Talk, now. - Okay. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.94,0:35:16.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天啊 讓我喘口氣\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Christ. Let me catch my breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.66,0:35:24.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們本來應該利用21響禮炮的槍聲\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We were supposed to use the gunfire from the 21-gun salute
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.79,0:35:25.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來掩蓋我們的射擊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to mask our shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.83,0:35:27.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干掉你和你的團隊成員\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Take you and your team down 
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.29,0:35:29.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在任何人搞清楚狀況前離開\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and get out of there before anyone knew what was going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.54,0:35:31.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對于專業槍手來說 賺這錢輕松容易\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Easy payday for a couple professional hitters.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.50,0:35:33.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- 跟我說些我不知道的事 - 比如\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- Tell me something I don't know. - Like what?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.75,0:35:36.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘭斯頓不會一開始就把所有錢都給你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Langston wouldn't give you all the cash up front.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.21,0:35:38.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要在哪里見他拿尾款\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where are you supposed to meet him to get the rest of the money?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.67,0:35:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇后區某個破爛街區的 一棟廢棄建筑里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}An abandoned building in some shitty neighborhood in Queens.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.80,0:35:43.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以帶你們去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Look, I-I can take you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.89,0:35:45.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我不認識蘭斯頓\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I don't know any Langston.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.85,0:35:47.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是誰雇的你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then who hired you?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.43,0:35:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個叫斯旺的家伙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Some guy called Swan.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.86,0:35:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Copy that.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.90,0:36:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪克森和奧唐納已就位 拉索在街上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Dixon and O'Donnell are in position. Russo's down the street.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.20,0:36:05.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有出口都已覆蓋\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All exits are covered.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.66,0:36:08.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽到了嗎  你要是敢亂來 你會后悔的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hear that? You try anything, you'll be sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.66,0:36:11.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你進去拿錢 給我們這地方的信息\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But you go in there, get paid, give us the rundown...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.04,0:36:13.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里面有多少人 他們帶著什么武器\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How many inside, what they're packing...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.33,0:36:15.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,房間的布局 人都坐在哪里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Layout of the room, where everyone's sitting...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.54,0:36:18.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后我們就放了你 你可以留著錢 懂了嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We'll cut you loose and you get to keep the cash. Understood?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.96,0:36:21.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 隨便吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, man. Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.17,0:36:23.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只希望永遠都不會再見到你們\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I just never want to see you people again.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.72,0:36:25.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你的手機給我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Give me your phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.48,0:36:36.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這個放在口袋里 這樣我們就能監聽\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Keep this in your pocket so we can listen in.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.15,0:36:39.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要是敢做小動作 我們會突然進攻 你就跟他們一起死吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You try anything, we come in hot and you die with the rest of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.53,0:36:41.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧 蠢貨\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Get going, stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.45,0:36:52.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們在想什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, what are we thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.21,0:36:54.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯旺去新時代工作\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Swan went to work for New Age,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.46,0:36:57.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了他一直夢寐以求的賺錢機會 然后就接受了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}saw a chance to make the kind of money he always dreamed of and took it?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.84,0:36:58.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Then what?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.75,0:37:01.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他跟弗朗茨一起出去玩 他們都在一個城市\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He was hanging out with Franzy, them being in the same city and all,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.59,0:37:04.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不小心透露了什么 讓弗朗茨產生了懷疑\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}slipped and said something that made Franz suspicious?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.80,0:37:08.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者他試著拉弗朗茨入伙\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Or... tried to get Franz in on it?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.97,0:37:11.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心想要養老婆和孩子 他也需要錢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Figured with a wife and kid, he'd need the money, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.43,0:37:13.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗朗茨拒絕了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Franz said no,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.31,0:37:16.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,試圖阻止 打電話給 桑切斯和奧羅斯科求助\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}tried to stop it, called Sanchez and Orozco for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.98,0:37:18.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那聽起來對嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That sound about right?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.03,0:37:22.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道 但如果斯旺真在那棟樓里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't know, but if Swan's really in that building,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.24,0:37:24.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也會像對待那家伙一樣對待斯旺\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm gonna do the same thing I did to that guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.53,0:37:27.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用手掐住他的脖子 從他嘴里榨出真相\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wrap my hand around his neck and squeeze the truth out of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.91,0:37:28.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之后呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And after that?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.58,0:37:35.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.38,0:37:38.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Anyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.18,0:39:55.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,字幕翻譯: 匡思穎
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.18,0:39:57.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,創意監督 朝思

